mod1.mod_description: VisualV Remastered is a captivating modification for Grand Theft Auto V Legacy that revitalizes the game's urban landscape with a fresh, atmospheric overhaul. As depicted in the image, this mod introduces a vibrant nighttime cityscape featuring illuminated buildings, bustling streets, and a starry sky, creating a lively yet serene ambiance. With enhanced lighting, detailed architecture, and a modern aesthetic, Project: Revive breathes new life into Los Santos, offering players an immersive and visually striking experience that elevates the game's original environment.

mod2.mod_description: Step back into neon-soaked nights and pastel-sunset streets with the “Vice City visuals” remake of VisualV for Grand Theft Auto V: a full overhaul that re-tones time of day, weather, lighting and colour grading to capture that iconic 1980s Miami-vice aesthetic. Expect crisp skies, saturated twilight hues, bold reflections, sharper shadows and a cinematic glow that turns Los Santos into a retro-dreamboard of palm trees, neon signs and midnight drives. Compatible with the original VisualV base, this legacy version channels classic vibes while retaining top-tier visual fidelity.

mod16.mod_description: VisualV Winter: Graphics Overhaul is the specialized seasonal component for the acclaimed VisualV graphics modification. It provides a comprehensive overhaul of Los Santos' visual fidelity, re-tuning the entire atmosphere to perfectly complement a winter environment; this mod fundamentally adjusts the game's core rendering to create an authentic winter mood, featuring Rewritten Weather cycles simulating a cold, overcast climate, eliminating the harsh California sun in favor of soft, diffused light. Atmospheric Realism is enhanced through volumetric fog, resulting in a dramatic, cold haze over the city; Lighting Correction adjusts tone mapping to produce cooler, more muted colors; and Enhanced Draw Distance allows the winter landscape to appear vast and richly detailed, making this mod essential for achieving the most realistic and atmospheric winter playthrough in GTA V.

mod3.mod_description:
IMPORTANT! Make sure all your GTA V graphics settings are on the lowest possible!

VenxPvP Graphics is a highly optimized graphical mod designed to give you a significant FPS boost without sacrificing too much visual clarity.

By meticulously adjusting shadows, reflections, particle effects, and more, this mod strips away unnecessary visual overhead to ensure your frame rate remains high and stable, which is absolutely critical for fluid, responsive PvP gameplay.

mod15.mod_description: This mod completely transforms the atmosphere of Los Santos for the holidays. It's an immersive seasonal mapping overhaul that replaces standard streetlights across the map with festive Christmas streetlights. Additionally, it brings extensive Christmas mapping, adding props, decorations, and seasonal visuals throughout Los Santos.

mod4.mod_description: LA Roads Remastered gives Los Santos a complete street-level makeover, replacing outdated textures with ultra-detailed, high-definition asphalt, brick intersections, and authentic Los Angeles-style lane markings. Expect crisp road surfaces, realistic wear patterns, and vibrant urban detailing that make the city feel freshly paved and alive. Perfect for players chasing realism without sacrificing performance, this remaster blends seamlessly with other visual mods for a clean, modern aesthetic.

mod5.mod_description: Europe Roads transforms Los Santos with authentic European-style road textures, markings, and asphalt patterns. From crisp lane dividers to realistic tarmac wear, it brings a continental vibe to every drive—perfect for players who want Los Santos to feel more like Paris than Pacific Coast Highway.

mod6.mod_description: LS: Real Locations brings the real-world landmarks and iconic storefronts of Los Santos into razor-sharp focus. This mod replaces generic generic-store facades with recognizable brands and textures, repositions and redesigns points of interest to more faithfully reflect their real-life counterparts, and altogether gives the city a layer of authenticity that doesn’t feel like just another flashy skin. Ideal for players who want immersion over spectacle.

mod7.mod_description: Give every cash machine in Los Santos a fresh facelift and deeper immersion with ATMs Reimagined. The mod replaces generic ATM props with high-detail models, updated textures, realistic bank branding, lighting effects and subtle sound cues, turning each withdrawal point into a believable part of the urban landscape rather than a bland static sign. Perfect for players who want the little details to pop while they’re cruising through the city.

mod8.mod_description: Billboards Reimagined is the essential visual mod for your GTA V Legacy experience. This modification replaces all the original, vanilla billboards and advertisements across Los Santos and Blaine County with a meticulously curated selection of real-life brand billboards.

mod9.mod_description: Face and Body Improvements overhauls character models with refined facial textures, enhanced skin detail, and subtle anatomical updates for both male and female characters. Expect sharper features, realistic complexion tones, visible muscle definition, and reimagined body mapping that modernizes GTA V’s character visuals without breaking immersion. It’s a tasteful evolution of the game’s look—more lifelike, less plastic.

mod10.mod_description: Winter Minimap Animated adds a frosty twist to your HUD with icy blue health and armor bars, animated indicator text, and gentle snowflakes that fall when you take damage. A small detail that makes every firefight feel like a snowstorm.

mod11.mod_description: Get rid of the clutter! This mod delivers a super clean, minimalist HUD for your game. It replaces the standard radar with a sleek, monochrome minimap showing only essential routes, and simplifies your Health and Armor into small, crisp indicators.

mod13.mod_description: This mod is a focused quality-of-life and aesthetic enhancement for combat. It reskins the Health and Armor bars to a high-contrast pink/magenta color. Crucially, the mod implements a dynamic text display that instantly flashes the player's exact numerical Health Points (HP) when damage is taken, providing immediate and precise combat feedback.

mod14.mod_description: This mod is a focused quality-of-life and aesthetic enhancement for combat. It reskins the Health and Armor bars to a high-contrast pink/magenta color. Crucially, the mod implements a dynamic text display that instantly flashes the player's exact numerical Health Points (HP) when damage is taken, providing immediate and precise combat feedback.

mod12.mod_description:
Elevate your aim and dominate in player-versus-player combat with the Plus Crosshair mod! This essential visual enhancement replaces your default in-game reticle with a sharp, classic plus-sign crosshair. Designed for maximum clarity and precision, it gives you a distinct and stable focal point, crucial for landing those critical shots.

Ideal for PvP: Gain an edge in firefights with a clear, unambiguous crosshair that helps you track targets and make every shot count.
